<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFEC6A53FD3393261A4FBD0C" pageId="23" pageNumber="781" type="discussion">
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFEC6A53FD3393261DE7BE92" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1915" box="[719,999,1407,1440]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Pipistrellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="781" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="paterculus">Pipistrellus paterculus</taxonomicName>
has been included as a subspecies or synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFEC6A53FBB193FE1AE9BEFA" box="[1101,1257,1447,1480]" class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Pipustrellus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="23" pageNumber="781" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="javanicus">P. javanicus</taxonomicName>
but is generally recognized as a distinct species based on morphological and genetic data. Two subspecies recognized.
</subSubSection>
</paragraph>
