No information.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFEC6A53FF979CCC1A7FB037" pageId="23" pageNumber="781" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFEC6A53FF979CCC1A7FB037" blockId="23.[105,1311,1731,2940]" pageId="23" pageNumber="781">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFFEC6A53FF979CCC1FC9B184" bold="true" box="[107,457,2709,2742]" pageId="23" pageNumber="781">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. There are currently no major threats affecting the Mount Popa Pipistrelle, but localized deforestation from logging and agricultural expansion might be a future threat.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
